data.description: Big Price Drop! As of 11/23 this is the lowest price single family home in Maricopa County w/ a 4 car garage, separate guest house and over 3000sf.  Wonderful 4 bed/3.5 bath home located in one of the most sought after neighborhoods in Queen Creek and includes a 4 Car Garage, RV Gate, 12,600sf Lot and Separate Guest House. The Main House Features  3 Bedrooms+Den, 2.5 Bathrooms, Cathedral Ceilings in the Great Room and 10 foot throughout the rest of the home w/ 8 foot doors, Coffered Ceilings in the Formal Dining, Den and Master Suite. The Spacious Kitchen consist of Granite Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, Gas Cooktop, Dual Ovens, Walk-in Pantry and Plenty of Cabinet Space. Incredible Master Suite with an Awesome Master Bathroom that Includes Dual Head Walk-In Shower, Freestanding Soaking Tub, and Two Large Walk In Closets. The Guest House has a Courtyard with Pavers and can be used as a Mother-in-Law Suite, Office or Exercise Room. The front yard was recently remodeled with new plants, trees and artificial grass. This home has a VA loan at a 4.25% interest rate and may be Assumable by a Veteran but only if he/she is willing to formally substitute their entitlement for the sellers on the mortgage. Buyer may have to qualify.
